title: Im trying to eject the SD external memory card in my newer phone so i can remove it. Its Galaxy a10e
content: Ive ejected and then removed a many SD cards from at least 5 diff makes but with this Galaxy a10e i cant even find in the sys setting a 'storage' header like with the other makes. They had a category in settings. . Simple, easily - user friendly (thought into and with the ops design and user abilities
